## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible strategies APRNs can use to encourage nursing-based outcome studies. Additionally, the search was limited to English-language sources and may not reflect global practices comprehensively. Further research could explore more diverse perspectives and include empirical studies to validate the proposed strategies.